Global Mobile Phone Chargers Market Insights
Mobile Phone Chargers Market size was valued at USD 30.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 48.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.


Mobile Phone Chargers Market Overview
The mobile phone chargers market was valued at USD 17.2 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is driven by rising smartphone adoption and technological advancements in charging solutions. The market is also influenced by the increasing demand for fast-charging and wireless charging technologies. Regionally, North America and Europe are the dominant markets, while emerging economies like Asia-Pacific are witnessing rapid growth due to a surge in mobile device usage and improved access to electronics.

